315
00:17:00,958 --> 00:17:04,250
Right. You go ahead make that
call. I'll leave you alone now.

316
00:17:04,333 --> 00:17:05,791
Till next time.

317
00:17:12,041 --> 00:17:13,125
All right.

318
00:17:17,083 --> 00:17:18,791
H-h-hello?! Morisato?!
Can you hear me?!

319
00:17:18,875 --> 00:17:21,250
It's me, Yoji Haneda! Say
something if you're there!

320
00:17:21,333 --> 00:17:23,250
Hey. Calm down, moron?

321
00:17:23,333 --> 00:17:25,333
Sorry we haven't
talked in so long.

322
00:17:25,416 --> 00:17:27,000
What's it been,
since freshman year?

323
