Hayato and I actually saw
each other quite a bit.

324
00:17:29,958 --> 00:17:31,291
Kakeru told me the news.

325
00:17:31,375 --> 00:17:33,833
I'm not sure that I really
get it, but you've unified

326
00:17:33,916 --> 00:17:35,458
