messed up. Seriously.

337
00:17:58,375 --> 00:18:01,250
Look, I consider you to be
a very good friend, Kazuma.

338
00:18:01,333 --> 00:18:04,416
And so, if you don't feel
the same way that I do.

339
00:18:04,500 --> 00:18:06,500
I'll just double down
on my affections!

340
00:18:06,583 --> 00:18:09,083
The way I feel about you will
