341
00:18:09,166 --> 00:18:10,083
it'll be perfect!

342
00:18:10,166 --> 00:18:11,916
You're talkin' like a stalker!

343
00:18:12,000 --> 00:18:14,041
Is that bad? I mean,
what's a stalker,

344
00:18:14,125 --> 00:18:16,291
but someone who
really really loves you?

345
00:18:16,375 --> 00:18:23,916
I get it! Enough! You know that
club, "Hetero"? Stop on by.

346
00:18:24,000 --> 00:18:26,375
We'll talk, catch up some.

347
00:18:26,458 --> 00:18:27,833
Mmm, sounds good!

348
00:18:29,333 --> 00:18:31,125
By the way, there's one
more important thing

349
00:18:31,208 --> 00:18:32,416
I need to tell you.

350
00:18:32,500 --> 00:18:34,000
Huh? Lay it on me?

351
00:18:34,083 --> 00:18:35,958
I don't know if
I should, actually.

352
00:18:36,041 --> 00:18:39,000
What the hell, you can't
wuss out on me like that now.

353
00:18:39,083 --> 00:18:41,625
All right.

354
00:18:41,708 --> 00:18:44,583
That stupid long hair of yours
makes you look like a douche!

355
