Yeah, says who?!

356
00:18:45,708 --> 00:18:47,125
Says everybody!

357
00:18:47,208 --> 00:18:49,333
I'm just telling you this
for your own good, man.

358
00:18:49,416 --> 00:18:50,875
As your friend!
People all call you

359
00:18:50,958 --> 00:18:53,541
