00:19:22,958 --> 00:19:23,833
Flame.

371
00:19:23,916 --> 00:19:25,250
Birdes.

372
00:19:25,333 --> 00:19:26,958
Yeah!

373
00:19:27,958 --> 00:19:29,750
Eeesh, you have
