374
00:19:30,916 --> 00:19:32,041
Huh?

375
00:19:32,125 --> 00:19:33,500
Guess I'll see ya around!

376
00:19:33,583 --> 00:19:34,708
Wha.

377
00:19:34,791 --> 00:19:36,708
Wait up, guys!

378
00:19:36,791 --> 00:19:38,416
Thank you, Kazuma.

379
00:19:38,500 --> 00:19:42,500
My friendship with you
ultimately led me to her.

380
00:19:42,583 --> 00:19:44,041
Hey. Who was that girl?

381
00:19:45,875 --> 00:19:47,666
When I turned around,
there she was!

382
00:19:47,750 --> 00:19:49,416
Well then, who might this be?

383
00:19:49,500 --> 00:19:52,416
Allow me to introduce
myself. I am Yoji Haneda.

384
00:19:56,125 --> 00:19:58,416
Would you mind not further
complicating the image

385
00:19:58,500 --> 00:19:59,666
I have of Takashi?!

386
00:19:59,750 --> 00:20:03,250
My mistake, I'll never
do it again. Uh.

387
00:20:03,333 --> 00:20:05,291
'Kay, get ready!

