392
00:20:21,166 --> 00:20:23,208
Enough of that, though,
how are my listeners doing?

393
00:20:23,291 --> 00:20:24,916
Believe it or not,
the Condor lives!

394
00:20:25,000 --> 00:20:26,875
Surely everyone remembers
my tragically heroic death

395
00:20:26,958 --> 00:20:29,083
in episode eight! But
appearances can be deceiving,

396
00:20:29,166 --> 00:20:31,791
as true legends like the Condor
are not limited by mere notions

397
00:20:31,875 --> 00:20:34,500
of life and death! Still, I
appreciate all of your fan mail

398
00:20:34,583 --> 00:20:36,375
and "Condor-lences,"
and appreciate those who

399
00:20:36,458 --> 00:20:39,416
