400
00:20:39,500 --> 00:20:41,541
And now I leave you with this
final nugget of wisdom--

401
00:20:41,625 --> 00:20:43,833
an egg of wisdom, rather.
Fry it, scramble it, boil it,

402
00:20:43,916 --> 00:20:45,583
but whatever you do,
take it to heart!

403
00:20:45,666 --> 00:20:47,291
Really, the yolk's
healthier than you think!

404
00:20:47,375 --> 00:20:49,750
Are you listening? Here goes:

405
00:20:49,833 --> 00:20:51,541
Don't be afraid to turn
the channel in life.

406
00:20:51,625 --> 00:20:53,875
Sure, the radio or TV may come
with presets, and you may find

407
00:20:53,958 --> 00:20:55,833
yourself compelled to keep
the dial centered on what's

408
00:20:55,916 --> 00:20:58,333
already there for you,
but don't sell yourself short!

409
00:20:58,416 --> 00:20:59,666
The direction of your
life is dependent

410
00:20:59,750 --> 00:21:01,083
on the channel you choose.

411
00:21:01,166 --> 00:21:03,666
If you don't like that channel,
then change it. Easy!

412
00:21:03,750 --> 00:21:05,041
Easier said
than done, you say?!

413
00:21:05,125 --> 00:21:07,000
Come on, I came back
from the dead!

414
00:21:07,083 --> 00:21:09,083
If I can self-resurrect,
then you've got no excuses

415
00:21:09,166 --> 00:21:10,416
for not flipping a knob!

416
00:21:10,500 --> 00:21:11,916
The world's a huge,
exciting place;

417
00:21:12,000 --> 00:21:13,875
no two channels are alike.

418
00:21:13,958 --> 00:21:15,916
So sit yourself down in
that metaphorical sofa

419
00:21:16,000 --> 00:21:18,333
and get to channel surfing!
Don't let those bullies

420
00:21:18,416 --> 00:21:21,208
and doubters hog the remote!
You control your destiny!

421
00:21:21,291 --> 00:21:23,166
Get rid of that inner
Naraku! And you thought

422
00:21:23,250 --> 00:21:24,916
I wouldn't bring
this back full circle!

423
00:21:25,000 --> 00:21:26,833
Pah, Condor's a professional!

424
00:21:26,916 --> 00:21:28,666
That's right, if you learn
anything from this story,

425
00:21:28,750 --> 00:21:30,541
please learn that you
control yourself.

426
00:21:30,625 --> 00:21:32,833
Also learn that the
Condor can't be destroyed.

427
00:21:32,916 --> 00:21:34,833
Invincible, I tell
you! Invincible!

428
00:21:34,916 --> 00:21:36,833
I kid, that's secondary.
Sort of. Don't get in a rut,

429
00:21:36,916 --> 00:21:39,041
be true to yourself,
and you'll do just fine.

430
00:21:42,708 --> 00:21:45,625
People were not meant
to live a lonely life.

431
00:21:45,708 --> 00:21:48,375
Remember that, and be
reassured that your brethren

432
00:21:48,458 --> 00:21:51,000
are always there at your side.

433
00:21:51,083 --> 00:21:54,875
We are not angels, and we
cannot soar through the sky.

434
00:21:54,958 --> 00:21:59,125
Even so, that does not mean we
cannot at least flap our wings.

435
00:21:59,208 --> 00:22:02,083
I'm positive that if
you all join together,

436
00:22:02,166 --> 00:22:06,375
your life on this Earth can be
enjoyable. I'm certain of it.

437
00:22:06,458 --> 00:22:11,583
After all, it would seem that
not all of us are without wings.

438
00:22:16,166 --> 00:22:19,500
Hey, you made it! Thanks for
sticking with me for so long.

439
00:22:19,583 --> 00:22:23,000
Our story's more or less over.
Well, that's not entirely true;

440
00:22:23,083 --> 00:22:24,541
it's technically
still going on,

441
00:22:24,625 --> 00:22:27,666
but we just don't have enough
time to go over everything.

442
00:22:27,750 --> 00:22:29,958
Long story short, we all
started living life with

443
00:22:30,041 --> 00:22:32,666
an eye towards the future.
Oh! You might find this

444
00:22:32,750 --> 00:22:35,708
kind of interesting, in my
studies I found out that people

445
00:22:35,791 --> 00:22:38,708
like you are what experts
call "Inner Self Helpers",

446
00:22:38,791 --> 00:22:41,791
or I-S-H for short.

447
00:22:41,875 --> 00:22:44,791
They basically take people who
have fallen apart, like us,

448
00:22:44,875 --> 00:22:46,208
and help piece
them back together,

449
00:22:46,291 --> 00:22:49,333
granting some
much-needed relief.

450
00:22:49,416 --> 00:22:51,291
We couldn't have
done it without you.

451
00:22:51,375 --> 00:22:56,583
So, on behalf of all of us,
I thank you. Keep it up!

452
00:23:01,458 --> 00:23:04,083
What's the deal, do we start
going to the same school today?

453
00:23:04,166 --> 00:23:07,000
No, silly! I just need to go
so I can fill your teachers

454
00:23:07,083 --> 00:23:11,041
