in on your situation.

455
00:23:11,125 --> 00:23:12,625
Surprise!

456
00:23:15,416 --> 00:23:17,083
Come on. Bring out Takashi!

457
00:23:17,166 --> 00:23:18,291
But, I can't!

458
00:23:18,375 --> 00:23:20,833
Guess I'll have
to slug you first!

459
00:23:20,916 --> 00:23:22,458
Don't you think it's
a little too early

460
00:23:22,541 --> 00:23:24,291
