461
00:23:24,375 --> 00:23:27,291
Aw, aren't you just adorable.
I wish I had a little sister

462
00:23:27,375 --> 00:23:30,791
as cute as you. But that doesn't
mean I'm eager to marry

463
00:23:30,875 --> 00:23:32,875
into the family or anything!

464
00:23:32,958 --> 00:23:37,125
Oh. I think. If I had an older
sister that was just like you.

465
00:23:37,208 --> 00:23:38,833
I'd never be sad again!

466
00:23:38,916 --> 00:23:40,916
Oh my gosh, she is so precious.

467
00:23:41,000 --> 00:23:42,083
You think so, huh?

468
00:23:42,166 --> 00:23:44,500
I'll follow you to
the ends of the Earth!

469
00:23:46,166 --> 00:23:48,375
I spotted you conversating
from a distance and it looked

470
00:23:48,458 --> 00:23:51,333
much too interesting to pass up!
So I hightailed it over here

471
00:23:51,416 --> 00:23:53,166
fast as I could, good
thing these tires were

472
00:23:53,250 --> 00:23:55,375
built for speed!
Am I too late?

473
00:23:55,458 --> 00:23:57,708
No matter, I'll just
start a new subject!

474
00:23:57,791 --> 00:24:00,541
So Kakeru and I had some
stew yesterday for lunch.

475
00:24:00,625 --> 00:24:02,541
Come to think of it, can
you still smell the garlic

476
00:24:02,625 --> 00:24:03,875
on my breath?

477
00:24:03,958 --> 00:24:05,958
Maybe if I get my lips
close enough to your nose

478
00:24:06,041 --> 00:24:08,875
and breathe out, the spirit
of Drac will take over!

479
00:24:08,958 --> 00:24:12,916
Guess I might as well try it.

480
00:24:13,000 --> 00:24:14,333
No ya' don't!

481
00:24:15,958 --> 00:24:18,625
Apparently there's some demand
for me to put out another book.

482
00:24:18,708 --> 00:24:21,166
Do you mind if I ask
you for some advice?

483
00:24:21,250 --> 00:24:23,958
If it weren't for Shusuke's
article on 88th Birthday,

484
00:24:24,041 --> 00:24:26,625
